                     <div class="row" style="text-align: center;  background-color: #F1F1F1;margin-top:3%; padding-top:2%;">
                        <h4 style="color: #233835" class="">Submit your Application</h4>
                        <p class="">​We are always looking for bright minds and enthusiastic people from diverse backgrounds, who want to be part of an outstanding team.<br/>Even if you don’t find a suitable position below, please do not hesitate to drop us your resume.
                        <br/><a class="btn btn-success" t-attf-href="/apply/default/" style="color:#ffffff; border:none; background-color: #FEBC11; width:80px;margin: 20px;text-align: center;">Apply</a>
                        </p>
